Movie Info: Ramaiya Vastavaiya is a 2013 Bollywood romance comedy film directed by Prabhu Deva. The film introduces producer Kumar Taurani's son Girish Kumar, opposite Shruti Haasan. It will be a remake of Prabhu Deva's directorial debut Telugu blockbuster Nuvvostanante Nenoddantana which in turn was inspired by the 1980s Hindi movie Maine Pyaar Kiya, though this film also features many similarities with the 1998 Hindi hit Pyaar Kiya To Darna Kya. The theatrical trailer of Ramaiya Vastavaiya was uploaded on 25 April 2013, whilst the film released on 19 July 2013.


